      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity study comparing at least two hemolysis power-law model forms; selection justified against experimental data.",
      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was applied. Comparative evaluation against the Zhang model not performed. Significant model-form uncertainty remains unquantified at MRL 5. Epistemic gap flagged."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
